<i>adverb</i>: 느슨히 [느슨히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>느슨히 [느슨히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. loosely</dd><br>
<dd>잡아매거나 묶은 끈, 매듭 등이 살짝 풀어져 헐거운 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loose state as a tied string or knot, etc., which has come slightly undone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. loosely</dd><br>
<dd>나사가 꽉 죄어져 있지 않아 헐거운 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loose state as a screw which is not tightly fastened.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slackly</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 긴장감이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without tension in the mind.</dd><br>
<dd>4. loosely; negligently</dd><br>
<dd>규제나 제도 등이 엄격하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a regulation, system, etc., being not strict.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>